Name: Mopidy-Rstation
Version: 1.0.0
Summary: Mopidy extension to show info on a display and control from it
Home-page: https://github.com/araczkowski/mopidy-rstation
Author: araczkowski
Author-email: araczkowski@gmail.com
License: Apache License, Version 2.0
Description: ******************
        Mopidy-rstation
        ******************
        
        Extension for remotely controlling Mopidy
        
        Dependencies
        ============
        
        - ``Mopidy`` >= 1.0
        - ``Pykka`` >= 1.1
        
        
        Installation
        ============
        
        Install by running::
        
            clone rstation
        
            cd rstation
        
            pip install . --upgrade
        
        
        Basic Configuration
        ===================
        
        Before starting Mopidy, you must add configuration for
        Mopidy-Rstation to your Mopidy configuration file::
        
            [rstation]
            enabled = true
        
